<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      .container {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .warning {
        color: red;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="warning">⚠️ Low Inventory Alert</h2>
      <p>Dear Admin,</p>
      <p>The inventory for <strong><%= @item.name %></strong> has dropped below the safe threshold.</p>
      <p>Current quantity: <strong><%= @item.quantity %></strong></p>

      <p>Please take appropriate action to restock this item at the earliest.</p>

      <p>Regards,<br>
      Cloud Kitchen System</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>